CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 29, 1946, pg. 22, reads: "From Higher Institutions - Having completed their training in institutions of higher learning, these students are prepared to take over the job of teaching the younger generation... Miss Helen Elizabeth Smith, who is the first student to receive the Robert L. Vann four-year scholarship, is in the center photo.  She received a Bachelor of Science degree from the University of Pittsburgh School of Education..."
TitMainTitle: University of Pittsburgh graduate Helen Elizabeth Smith (Faison) posed with diploma in front of Cathedral of Learning, Oakland
